In order to run the script :-
- use system call "make mycat".
- Then, to run the script using user input :-
	- Type "./mycat" then press Enter.
	- Enter the text you want to use, then press Enter.
- To run the script using input from file :-
	- Type "./mycat filename". then press Enter.
- To use the grep command :-
	- Type "./mycat <filename> | grep string" then press Enter.
